topicText:
Footballers pay tribute to Moroccan boy Rayan after tragic death
Clubs and players expressed condolences to the family of Rayan Oram, who died after being stuck in a well for five days.
Death of Moroccan boy in well draws sympathy from around world
Rayan Oram, five, was found dead after four-day operation to rescue him from shaft 32 metres deep.
Haunting final words of boy in well
The tragic final words of a five-year-old boy who died after being trapped in a well in Morocco for days has been revealed.
